<h1>About Wildlife Explorer</h1>
<p>This application catalogs animals, their habitats, and observations. Data is sourced from genuine CSV files and Faker, ensuring realistic content.</p>

<h2>ER Diagram</h2>
<%= image_tag "diagram.png", alt: "ER Diagram for Wildlife Explorer", class: "img-fluid" %>
<p>The diagram above illustrates the database schema for our project. It shows the relationships between the <strong>Animal</strong>, <strong>Habitat</strong>, <strong>Observation</strong>, and the join table <strong>AnimalHabitat</strong>. Animals can have multiple observations and belong to multiple habitats, providing a flexible structure for data navigation and integration.</p>
